            - D O O M E D   H O R I Z O N   S O F T W A R E -

Welcome to the Doomed Horizon ordering progam! It's so easy to use!
Just double click on it and use the intuative GUI to enter your details
regarding your name, address, email, the Doomed Horizon titles you wish
to order and the currency you wish to pay in. You may pay by cash or
Postal Order in whatever currency you select (There's no need to change
it to Irish money!)
				The software titles Doomed Horizon offers the Amiga
community are unparalled in quality and ease of use. We strife to produce
a comprehensive range of leisure software which is both useful and
interesting. Although our range is currently only limeted to about 10 or
11 titles, with your support we will be producing more and better products
in the future.
			Doomed Horizon are a fledgeling Irish software company
totally dedicated to the Amiga and its survival, specialising in the more
artistic end of software. We intend to breathe a new lease of life into
the Amiga software world, by creating new concepts in interactive and
gaming software.

